32 section number to read consecutively.
33 SUMMARY
3344 This amendment, which is the majority report of the committee, replaces the resolve
3355 and changes the title. It establishes the Working Group on Modernizing State Grants,
3366 Contracts and Procurement to examine the State's grant and public procurement practices
3377 and make recommendations to the Department of Administrative and Financial Services.
3388 The working group is required to submit a report, which may include recommendations for
3399 legislation, by November 4, 2026 to the joint standing committee of the Legislature having
4400 jurisdiction over state and local government matters, the Department of Administrative and
